{"tid":2094311,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[兩分鐘學識] 日式照燒三文魚","createTime":"2020-07-04T13:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T15:16:09.000Z","uid":333435,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7d3662dc2f5b57b1413c045ba459edfb54a9dd74","tid":2094311,"uid":333435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T13:55:55.000Z","msg":"成日出街食飯貴，係屋企煮又想食日本野?<br />\n簡簡單單煮番道日式照燒三文魚就岩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由準備到放入口食只需十分鐘，幾懶都整倒！<br />\n魚肉嫩滑，照燒汁帶甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗起都流口水<br />\n如果有興趣就click入條片了解詳細食譜啦!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/396jhrh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F396jhrh.jpg&h=54e17bf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/K7IHlW-qWtk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FK7IHlW-qWtk&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=ccbba140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/K7IHlW-qWtk</a><br />\n<br />\n多謝各位巴絲打支持！鐘意我地教學嘅可以俾個like同subscribe 我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;有咩想學都可以留言講啊！<br />\n<br />\n上回教學：<br />\n梅菜扣肉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2092869\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2092869</a><br />\n<br />\n豉油皇煎蝦碌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2089023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2089023</a><br />\n<br />\nKFC白汁雞皇飯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2084788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2084788</a>"},{"pid":"ea4c874de18386e0aef4ce9431088e676dc6db76","tid":2094311,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T13:57:22.000Z","msg":"我只想講，你整果個扣肉，直情係侮辱左扣肉呢個餸！👎🏻👎🏻👎🏻👎🏻👎🏻"},{"pid":"240befaff7a7425d9077410a0be5119ee764b63c","tid":2094311,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:00:31.000Z","msg":"絲打版 越煮越好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /